<div><head>楚竹書十一《仲弓》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.2">仲弓曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.3">「敢問事君。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.4">孔子<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.5">曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.6">「雍，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.7">古之事君者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.8">以忠與敬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.9">唯其難也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.10">汝惟以□其咎。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.11">仲弓曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.12">「今之君子，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.13">愎過捍析，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.14">難以納諫。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.15">孔子曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.16">「今之君子所竭其情、盡其質者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.17">三害近與矣。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.18">雍，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.19">汝知者。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.20">仲弓答曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.21">「雍也弗聞也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.22">孔子曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.23">「夫祭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.24">至敬之本也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.25">所以立生也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.26">不可不慎也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.27">夫喪至愛之卒也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.28">所以成死也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.29">不可不慎也；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.30">夫行踐仁孝不可不慎也之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.31">一日以善立，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.32">所學皆終；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.33">一日以不善立，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.34">所學皆崩，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.35">可不慎乎？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.36">仲弓曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.37">「今之君子使人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.38">不盡其悅<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.39">早使不行，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.40">綏&amp;CH-0F234C;上下相報以忠，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.41">則民歡承教，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.42">害□者不問民務。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.43">孔子曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.44">「善哉，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.45">聞乎是以教矣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.46">君飪。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.47">孔子曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.48">「唯政者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.49">正也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.50">夫子唯有與，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.51">汝獨正之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.52">豈不有枉也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.53">仲季桓子使仲弓為宰，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.54">仲弓以告孔子，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.55">孔子曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.56">「季氏<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.57">與聞之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.58">夫季氏，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.59">河東之盛家也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.60">亦使雍也從於宰夫之後，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.61">雍也童愚，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.62">恐貽吾子憂，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.63">愿因吾子而治。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.64">孔子曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.65">「雍汝以行矣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.66">為之眾謀汝。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.67">仲弓曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.68">「敢問為政何先？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.69">也定，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.70">不及其成。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.71">獨獨狷人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.72">難為從正。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.73">孔子毋自惰也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.74">昔三代之明王有四海之內，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.75">猶徠<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.76">老老慈幼，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.77">先有司，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.78">舉賢才，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.79">宥過與罪。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.80">，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.81">政之始也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.82">仲弓曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.83">「若夫老老慈幼，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.84">既聞命矣。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.85">夫先有司為之如何？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.86">仲尼曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.87">「夫民安舊而重遷有成，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.88">是故有司不可不先也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.89">仲弓曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.90">「雍也不敏，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.91">雖有賢才，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.92">弗知舉也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.93">敢問舉才如之何？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.94">仲尼：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.95">「夫賢才不可弇也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.96">舉爾所知，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.97">爾所不知，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.98">人其舍之者。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.99">仲弓曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.100">「宥過赦罪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.101">則民可畜<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.102">子有臣萬人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.103">導汝思老齊家，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.104">夫<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.105">服之緩，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.106">弛而遜力之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.107">雖有孝德，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.108">其<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.109">仲尼<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.110">山有崩，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.111">川有竭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.112">日月星辰猶佐，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.113">民亡不有過，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.114">賢者<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.115">宜順之至者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.116">教而使之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.117">君子亡所狷人。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.118">今汝相夫<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.119">中弓<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.120">刑政不緩，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.121">德教不倦。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.122">仲弓曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.123">「若此三者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.124">聞命矣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.125">敢問道民興德如何？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.126">孔子曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4539_CHANT_001-1a.127">「申之<lb/></seg>
</p>
